**Horrifying Wolf** | Werewolf Miscellaneous | Limited  
__Basics__
Whoever perceives the Horrifying Wolf may not investigate the following night. 
__Details__
If a player investigates the Horrifying Wolf at night, they are obstructed and may not investigate during the following night.
This applies even if a disguise or obstruction affects the investigation.

__Simplified__
Whoever perceives the Horrifying Wolf may not investigate the following night. 

__Formalized__
Inherit: `Pack Lycan`
On Visited [Investigating]: Process: Apply `Horrified` to @Visitor (~NextNight)

__Card__
The Horrifying Wolf will etch terror in the memory of anyone who meets its gaze.
